<div class="relative w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="relative">
    <div class="gradient gradient-left"></div>
    <div class="gradient gradient-right"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-32 mb-16 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <p class="text-sm text-black font-medium">A little bit</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About DPI</h1>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold italic mb-2">Discovery Partners Institute</h1>
    <p class="text-xl font-thin italic">empowers people to jumpstart their tech careers or companies</p>
    <p class="text-xl font-thin italic mb-5">in Chicago.</p>
    <%= link_to "Learn More", "https://dpi.uillinois.edu/", class: "inline-block bg-black text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors" %>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-12">
    <p class="text-base font-medium text-left">Give Back By</p>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-left mb-8">Becoming A DPI Mentor</h2>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <span class="font-bold">Discovery Partners Institute</span> (DPI) is training the next generation of Illinois's tech talent, 
        and we'd love to have your help. Our enthusiastic trainees are eager for positions where they can grow into 
        valuable leaders and community members, and they need someone like you to guide them on their journeys.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-8 gap-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
    <div class="col-span-3 row-span-2 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[320px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_1.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Mentor" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-5 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[150px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_2.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Program" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-2 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[150px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_3.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Initiative" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-3 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[150px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_4.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Community" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16 px-4">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">We're looking for leaders with:</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-1 text-lg italic">
      <li>At Least Four Years of Experience in Their Field</li>
      <li>Previous Background in Tech, Design, Or Business</li>
      <li>The Ability To Meet At Least Once Every Two Weeks</li>
      <li>The Ability To Attend At Least Six 30-Minute Meetings</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-20 px-4">
    <div class="ml-auto w-2/3">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <span class="font-bold">DPI mentorship is a great way to connect with our diverse talent from all walks of life.</span>
        You'll be guiding one or more Chicagoans through the unspoken rules of the business world and helping them
        find their footing in an ever-changing job market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">We place our trainees in various fields</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-8">Sales, Customer Success, Software Development, Project Management</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 justify-center items-center">
      <%= image_tag "companies/uls.svg", class: "h-10", alt: "ULS" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/sap.svg", class: "h-10", alt: "SAP" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/cibc.svg", class: "h-10", alt: "CIBC" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/united.svg", class: "h-10", alt: "United" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/hcsc.svg", class: "h-10", alt: "HCSC" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center mb-16 px-4">
    <p class="text-xl">
      Would you like to explore an alternative way to contribute?
      <span class="font-bold">Join us for a Riverside Chat!</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-20 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Riverside</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
      <p>
        <span class="font-bold">Get to know the DPI team</span> and hear from our
        talent network by joining us for a Riverside Chat! This is a casual question-and-answer
        session where our staff will explore your background and the "whys" behind your success.
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="font-bold">Riverside Chats</span> present a unique opportunity to meet our
        trainees and answer their insightful questions about your field of work. We've had
        cutting-edge leaders from companies like Salesforce, Capital One, and ShipBob join us for Riversides.
      </p>
      <p>
        Along with the trainees, we'll discuss how DPI can
        <span class="font-bold">boost your business</span> through our Tech Accelerator.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-32 px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-black">Make An Impact Today!</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="text-lg space-y-6">
        <p>
          Whether it's through mentorship or just a few hours at a Riverside Chat,
          you can permanently change the future of technology in Illinois. This small
          commitment can make a difference in someone's life and career trajectory.
        </p>
        <p>
          We appreciate your interest in spending time with DPI. If you'd like to
          learn more, please send an email and we'll be in touch soon.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Contact DPI", "mailto:info@dpi.dev", class: "inline-block bg-black text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>